  }, "Daniel Pianetti:")), mdx("p", null, "Design wise, it's always been a challenge. For example, we do find people who are new to the platform asking, okay, where are the sub folders? Can I create a sub folder? Because I have this directories mindset. We did through try to explore in the horizontality of it and try to focus design wise on the details and the single actions, and to make those as intuitive as they are. But yeah, I will say, especially, with onboarding new members, it's always a challenge to get them into the right space and understand, but eventually, they get it."), mdx("p", null, mdx("em", {
