  }, "Daniel Pianetti:")), mdx("p", null, "One thing I see often is initiatives that start within individual and developers, or small group of friends. And those are definitely things that go toward the direction. But it's hard to see something that really stays around for a long time. And they sometimes evolve into something or maybe this person gets hired by a company. And then that pro project becomes more like a hobby project, and then eventually dies."), mdx("p", null, mdx("em", {
