    parentName: "p"
  }, "Daniel Pianetti:")), mdx("p", null, "I was thinking about this among those individual projects that eventually get folded. Well, for sure patience was a big element of our success. And yeah, we just kept going. And I think as long as we see interest from our community and people not losing interest in it. Technically speaking, we have a very low churn rate of paying members and that's extremely encouraging for us. As long as we see the people stay on and they pay for eight, five years in a row, we know there's something and keeps it going."), mdx("p", null, mdx("em", {
