    parentName: "p"
  }, "Ethan Zuckerman:")), mdx("p", null, "Hey, everybody, welcome to Re-imagining the Internet. I'm Ethan Zuckerman, your host. Today, I have with us Sarita Schoenebeck, she's associate professor at the University of Michigan School of Information. She is director of the Living Online Lab, which has the wonderful acronym of LOL, and she is justly celebrated for really original and creative work on equity and justice in online spaces. Sarita, thanks so much for being with us."), mdx("p", null, mdx("em", {
