  }, "Ethan Zuckerman:")), mdx("p", null, "We had a wonderful interview on the show a couple of weeks back with the remarkable founders of Assembly For, which is an Australian collective of sex workers and allies who've built sweater as an alternative to Twitter to make it sex worker friendly. And of course they're doing this from a part of Australia where sex work is legal."), mdx("p", null, mdx("em", {
    parentName: "p"
