  }, "Lola Hunt:")), mdx("p", null, "I think yes and no."), mdx("p", null, mdx("em", {
    parentName: "p"
  }, "Eliza Sorensen:")), mdx("p", null, "I think yes and no, because one of the problems is, Facebook, in particular, are utilizing something called photoDNA or spotlight. Both of these programs are intertwined with Microsoft and Thorn. If we ought to be using these type of databases, they should be looked after by police, not private entities who have access to this material."), mdx("p", null, mdx("em", {
    parentName: "p"
  }, "Lola Hunt:")), mdx("p", null, "Who are run by... A lot of the people who are doing this, the moderation and things like that, are not on Facebook. On these sorts of programs, they're civilians. They're not people who have been trained specifically for those sorts of roles. I don't know how to handle that sort of material."), mdx("p", null, mdx("em", {
    parentName: "p"
  }, "Eliza Sorensen:")), mdx("p", null, "I think it's also just, ", "[cheerly 00:36:13]", " it's the responsibility of police."), mdx("p", null, mdx("em", {
