    parentName: "p"
  }, "Ethan Zuckerman:")), mdx("p", null, "So this is a huge long term shift. So for as much as we could admire Assembly Four, for building Switter. As an alternative building Tryst, sort of thinking about future projects and all of this. It sounds like the overall arc is sort of a cultural project, not just around sex work, but really about sex. And sort of changing attitudes, changing opinions. Is there a way that the internet works sort of plays into that as well?"), mdx("p", null, mdx("em", {
    parentName: "p"
