    parentName: "p"
  }, "Ethan Zuckerman:")), mdx("p", null, "That is incredible to hear. I'm not sure the credit's really due to me, but I will take it. Thank you so much for being with us, and this is just so exciting. I hope you get inquiries all over the world coming out of the conference, and I'm going to let you go do the opening. I look forward to being with you at it tomorrow, and thank you for being with us and re-imagining the internet."), mdx("p", null, mdx("em", {
