    "href": "https://www.wikipedia.org/"
  }, "Wikipedia"), " founder Jimmy Wales joins us for a thrilling chat about what we can learn from social media and what\u2019s anti-social about a lot of social media today. Jimmy has recently launched the the social network ", mdx("a", {
